divs: sighting detailsmyself,and my brother-in-law were returning to omaha following a star gazing evening east of louisville, ne. we were north bound on highway 50 at the interstste 80 interchange,when we had to detour due to accident.we had to go east to 126&harrison,now we are headed westbound,was stopped at red lite at 144th st.we noticed a very slow moving brite\intense white lite moving in our direction,from west to east\slightly north east,also noticed was short wings with two green lites strobing in unison.my brother-in-law joel stuck his upper body out of the window to follow object as it passed over us,what made this event strange was the fact that there was absoutely no sound coming from this object!!if this was our police helicopter it would have made lots of sound!!the estimated altitude was between 250 and 300 feet, again moving very slowly!! this also could not be a small aircraft,as it would have stalled out the foward speed was so slow!
